data.description: Beautiful well-kept 2 bedroom, 1 bath home on a desirable block in the very hot Port Richmond neighborhood boasts a recent kitchen overhaul, brand new water heater, newer house heater, upgraded electric, solid pine doors, hardwood floors and molding throughout.  Cute backyard area for grilling or chilling.  Just a short walk to public transportation, the Septa bus depot and everything else Port Richmond has to offer.  Not to mention that you are just 10 minutes outside of Center City without having to pay Center City prices! This one is a perfect starter home or investment property.  Come and take a look, you won’t be disappointed!
